      "data": {
        "title": "Checkpoint",
        "body": "You are done when you can say:\n- node classes make node structure reusable\n- edge classes make relationship semantics reusable\n- templates make graph arrangement reusable\n- bridges and authority boundaries help those artifacts travel safely",
